sequenceDiagram
    actor Customer
    participant Yves as Yves Storefront
    participant IAM as DTAG IAM (Empower ID)
    participant Strategy as Custom OAuth<br>Customer Strategy
    participant DB as Spryker DB

    Customer->>Yves: Request protected resource
    Yves->>Yves: No session detected
    Yves-->>Customer: Redirect to IAM (authorize)
    Customer->>IAM: Authenticate
    IAM-->>Customer: Redirect back with auth code
    Customer->>Yves: Return with auth code
    Yves->>IAM: Exchange code for tokens
    IAM-->>Yves: Access/ID tokens
    Yves->>Strategy: Resolve customer from token
    Strategy->>DB: Find/link customer + company/dealer context
    DB-->>Strategy: CustomerTransfer (with company relations)
    Strategy-->>Yves: Authenticated customer
    Yves->>Yves: Create session
    Yves-->>Customer: Access granted (dealer-scoped catalog)

    Note over Strategy: OOTB AcceptOnly / CreateCustomer<br>strategies insufficient for B2B —<br>custom strategy establishes company context
